videos.headline: Auburn strikes first against Washington
videos.description: Jarrett Stidham hits Sal Cannella for a 10-yard TD.

videos.headline: Browning intercepted by Auburn
videos.description: Auburn's Jamel Dean intercepts Jake Browning's pass.

videos.headline: Washington's 2nd-quarter strike closes gap on Auburn
videos.description: After a slow start, Jake Browning and the Huskies step it up in the second quarter scoring 10 points to inch within 2 of Auburn at the half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Washington’s 2nd-quarter strike closes gap on Auburn) 2018/9/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Washington WR fights off double coverage to make one-handed grab
videos.description: Washington WR Ty Jones makes a  one-handed sideline catch despite double coverage and pass interference.

videos.headline: Washington WR Jones makes second spectacular catch of the game
videos.description: Washington WR Ty Jones fights off pass interference for second time to make a spectacular catch.

videos.headline: Washington WR pulls in incredible one-handed touchdown catch
videos.description: Washington WR Quinten Pounds makes an unbelievable one-handed catch to cut deficit 15-13.

videos.headline: Auburn forces fumble in the red zone
videos.description: Auburn's Nick Coe forces a Jake Browning fumble in the red zone and is recovered by Darrell Williams.

videos.headline: Whitlow plows through defenders into the end zone to take lead
videos.description: Auburn RB JaTarvious Whitlow plows through defenders into the end zone to take 21-16 lead late in the forth.

videos.headline: Washington's Browning fumble overturned on field late in forth quarter
videos.description: Auburn big man takes off after a fumble recovery but the call is overturned to an incomplete pass.

videos.headline: Gus Malzahn and Auburn players try on old leather helmet after win
videos.description: Gus Malzahn and his Auburn players pass around the Old Leather Helmet Trophy after opening week win versus Washington.

videos.headline: Auburn takes down Washington in top-10 battle
videos.description: The No. 9 Tigers take the lead on JaTarvious Whitlow's 10-yard TD run and hold of the No. 6 Huskies to win 21-16.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Auburn takes down Washington in top-10 battle) 2018/09/01 ESHEET SOTFULL
